metadata.name: Knight Pass #1
metadata.description: Knight Pass represents our genesis, these will forever be important to the ecosystem, and the utility will grow as we reward those who have believed in us from the beginning. With a total supply of 1,110, the Knight pass is core proof of genesis ownership and governance of Knight DAO. The Lab offers two Knight Passes: The Divine 7 Pass, and the Divine 9 Pass. How deeply will you reach out and connect to the Knighty World?
